OL,3,CFarmer with giant hernia going private
OL,4,Cafter five year wait for NHS operation
OL,6,FGranada Reports correspondent Rob
OL,7,FSmith talks to Winston Baldwin about
OL,8,Fhis five year wait for a hernia
OL,9,Foperation on the NHS.
OL,11,FA former dairy farmer from Crewe, who
OL,12,Fhas been waiting for an NHS operation
OL,13,Fto fix a hernia for almost five years
OL,14,Fsays he has been let down by the NHS
OL,15,Fand will now have to go private.
OL,17,FWinston Baldwin, 75, has been living
OL,18,Fwith a triple hernia since 2019 which
OL,19,Fhas grown so large he can now barely
OL,20,Fwalk and has moved to a care home.
