OL,3,CFarmer with giant hernia going private
OL,4,Cafter five year wait for NHS operation
OL,6,FHis story has been featured on ITV
OL,7,FGranada Reports four times, ever since
OL,8,Fhis treatment was delayed in 2019
OL,9,Fduring Covid.
OL,11,FIn 2022, Winston was told his hernia
OL,12,Fwas too large to be operated on, but
OL,13,Fthere was a glimmer of hope in March
OL,14,F2023 when two surgeons from Arrowe
OL,15,FPark hospital on the Wirral got in
OL,16,Ftouch to say they could operate.
OL,18,FAlmost a year on though, Winston is
OL,19,Fstill waiting, despite having a number
OL,20,Fof pre-operation appointments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
