OL,3,CFarmer with giant hernia going private
OL,4,Cafter five year wait for NHS operation
OL,6,FNow he is going to finance the surgery
OL,7,Fhimself, he said: "I will go private,
OL,8,Fif it takes all my money I'm going
OL,9,Fprivate."
OL,11,F"Possibly in London, possibly in
OL,12,FOxford, possibly in Bristol, and I'll
OL,13,Ftake my chances there."
OL,15,FWinston said he hopes to have the
OL,16,Fsurgery as soon as possible.
