OL,3,CFarmer with giant hernia going private
OL,4,Cafter five year wait for NHS operation
OL,6,FPreviously, a Wirral University
OL,7,FTeaching Hospital spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"We can confirm our surgeons reached
OL,9,Fout to Mr Baldwin to offer their
OL,10,Fclinical expertise in order to help.
OL,12,F"Due to reasons of patient
OL,13,Fconfidentiality, we are unable to
OL,14,Fcomment further."
OL,16,FIt comes as a major review of the
OL,17,Fhealth service has found the NHS is in
OL,18,Fa "critical condition" and the health
OL,19,Fof the nation has "deteriorated" over
OL,20,Fthe last 15 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
