OL,3,CFarmer with giant hernia going private
OL,4,Cafter five year wait for NHS operation
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer announced the
OL,7,Fgovernment is working on a ten year
OL,8,Fplan with three key areas for reform -
OL,9,Fthe transition to a digital NHS,
OL,10,Fmoving more care from hospitals to
OL,11,Fcommunities, and focusing efforts on
OL,12,Fprevention over sickness.
OL,14,FEarlier this year, Granada Reports
OL,15,Fasked Sir Keir about Winston's five
OL,16,Fyear wait for a hernia operation and
OL,17,Fhe said it was a "shocking indictment"
OL,18,Fof NHS waiting lists.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
