OL,3,CFarmer with giant hernia going private
OL,4,Cafter five year wait for NHS operation
OL,6,FAt his carehome in Crewe, WInston says
OL,7,Freform of the NHS is essential: "Some
OL,8,Fareas of the NHS are very broken, some
OL,9,Fareas are good."
OL,11,F"I feel the NHS does need tweaking,
OL,12,Freforming, improving and it's not
OL,13,Fgoing to be a ten year plan, it's
OL,14,Fgoing to be forever."
OL,16,F"You don't steer a ship by looking at
OL,17,Fthe stars, you do it by steering."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
